{"tid":300961,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[一句到尾] 租定買?","createTime":"2017-06-28T10:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T10:48:29.000Z","uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abb8b7dcca2e6b50dd8a515398d66d75b98cafba","tid":300961,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:10:02.000Z","msg":"無論考慮咩因素都好, 我地用窮舉法, 最後只會有幾種情況, 你只會有幾個選擇, 即係足球界既 &quot;一係入一係唔入&quot; 黎總結所有情況<br />\n<br />\n樓價:<br />\n1. 大跌<br />\n2. 小跌<br />\n3. 橫行<br />\n4. 小升<br />\n5. 大升<br />\n<br />\n上述5種情況發生時間:<br />\n1. 2年後<br />\n2. 5年後<br />\n3. 10年後<br />\n4. 20年後<br />\n<br />\n選擇:<br />\n1. 長租<br />\n2. 即買 (居屋/私樓?)<br />\n3. 租住等佢跌先買 (咩時候跌幾多買? 5年後跌10% ? 10年後跌25%)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n窮舉上述所有情況, 計及租金支出 VS 供樓利息連雜費支出<br />\n<br />\n到底係咩情況下, 點樣做成本最低, 贏面最大?<br />\n<br />\n又係咩情況下, 9成機會輸?"},{"pid":"9def342bddfba44b26942f6b0770b9ab42720eb4","tid":300961,"uid":50491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d2132cf06f64b96d5a89b864312fd007c8c8a4","tid":300961,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"有冇自住樓<br />\n無既仲問既人就點極都唔醒架啦"},{"pid":"8f3bb6710c82b47aad92b59f8a8ab23721aab6f8","tid":300961,"uid":125688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"租樓日日賺, 人地長實樓王做左咁多年人都係首置,最緊要有老細照住"},{"pid":"2f7c56410a509a55503b835abd10a74a4a230f6b","tid":300961,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"好多人都係話租住先等跌，你身邊都應該有唔少咁既先知，結果佢地係錯失上車機會，再將原本既首期貼去交租，錯左又唔敢認，只有繼續租<br />\n<br />\n重覆犯錯！"},{"pid":"daa425b4b2391ac82184c56c50218dc031c0e8ed","tid":300961,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T10:48:29.000Z","msg":"租樓保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />